{
  "stem": "23096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then the ones that were still alive were just scattered throughout, you know, in the camp in various places.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were absolutely [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just walking skeletons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's all they were, no expression on their face, blank eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] Oh, god.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[CRYING] See, the worst part is I, I see all this stuff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I, [SOBBING] I can't get it out of my mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Most of them, they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very few of them, maybe one or two of them could talk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they were just-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know if they knew who we were or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they didn't show any emotion to, to what I could see-- maybe afterwards when they, you know, realized what was going on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] oh, man, it-- absolutely no expression, just gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I, I don't know who was in more shock, the prisoners or us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think most of the-- at-- the first few minutes, hour or so, everybody was just-- just seemed to be just wandering around, looking.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A couple, couple inmates did come and kind of show us around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We went into some of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were dead bodies all in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From what I understand now, when a person died, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the inmates had to dispose of the bodies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when, when the people became so weak that they couldn't, the bodies just laid there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you'd see a-- maybe a living person, a living corpse laying there and right next to them, maybe four or five dead ones.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You couldn't tell one from the other, except the one moved a little bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
